{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-475-music-festival","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Izazov 475: Muzički festival","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Muzičari $12n$ učestvuju na muzičkom festivalu. Prvog dana, formiraju grupe od osam $3n$ i vežbaju ceo dan.</p>\n<p>To je katastrofa. Na kraju dana, svi muzičari odlučuju da više neće prihvatiti sviranja sa bilo kojim članom njihove prethodne grupe.</p>\n<p>Drugog dana, formiraju grupe od tri $4n$, svaki muzičar izbegava svoje kolege iz prethodne grupe.</p>\n<p>To je broj načina za formiranje grupa od tri među muzičarima $f(12n)$ $12n$.</p>\n<p>Dobio sam $f(12) = 576$ i $f(24)\\bmod 1\\,000\\,000\\,007 = 509\\,089\\,824$.</p>\n<p>Izračunaj $f(600)\\bmod 1\\,000\\,000\\,007$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f5481000cf542c51005a","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302152,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-475-music-festival"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function musicFestival() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nmusicFestival();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>musicFestival()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>75780067</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(musicFestival(), 75780067);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-401-to-480","dashedName":"problem-475-music-festival","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPre